history.content: 162 is tough, so plenty of people will drop. With 408 people, 10% rule says roughly 41 will drop, but since it is a tough course, even more probably will, so I wouldn't worry. In general, you aren't gonna find answers though to whether a class will expand until it is announced. Advisors and professors have no reason not to announce once they know it is happening, and plenty of reasons not to announce if they aren't sure
I'm currently position 68 for CS162. I looked on the class notes on classes.berkeley.edu, but I couldn't find information about class expansion. Is 162 going to be expanded for SP20?
